ouleur qui permet au conducteur de se retourner sans problème. Cette « vielle » exemption qui date du temps où certaines ceintures ne disposaient pas d'un enrouleur a résisté au travers des années. Au nombre des dispenses au port obligatoire de la ceinture, on compte donc « les conducteurs qui effectuent une marche arrière ».</p>","audioText":null},"possibleAnswers":[{"__typename":"Answer","_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d7c0","gapIndex":null,"learningId":490218,"audioText":null,"text":"oui","isCorrect":true,"okulusAssets":[]},{"__typename":"Answer","_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d7c1","gapIndex":null,"learningId":491446,"audioText":null,"text":"non","isCorrect":false,"okulusAssets":[]}]}]},{"__typename":"Exercise","_id":"60b0bef6b80948a2bf97af3a","learningId":151608,"text":"","difficulty":1,"displayType":"","audioText":"","maxDurationSeconds":0,"okulusAssets":[],"questionsData":[{"__typename":"Question","learningId":142700,"score":{"__typename":"Score","success":0,"failure":1},"type":"QCM_SINGLE","okulusAssets":[{"__typename":"File","_id":"65711b81-1813-4c35-b8be-ec318ce7c0cd","version":"v0","mime":"audio/mpeg","filename":"65711b81-1813-4c35-b8be-ec318ce7c0cd","s3swhUrl":"https://diy7ta1tt6jst.cloudfront.net/prod/okulus/65711b81-1813-4c35-b8be-ec318ce7c0cd","realm":"digiSchool","imageTags":null},{"__typename":"File","_id":"3628bb8d-19bf-44d8-8f0c-5b3485297352","version":"v0","mime":"image/jpeg","filename":"3628bb8d-19bf-44d8-8f0c-5b3485297352","s3swhUrl":"https://diy7ta1tt6jst.cloudfront.net/prod/okulus/3628bb8d-19bf-44d8-8f0c-5b3485297352","realm":"digiSchool","imageTags":{"__typename":"ImageTags","width":1224,"height":816,"format":"JPEG"}}],"_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d79e","text":"Pendant la manoeuvre de marche arrière, sont exemptés du port de la ceinture :","audioText":null,"explanation":{"__typename":"Explanation","text":"<p>En cas de marche arrière, seul le conducteur est dispensé du port de la ceinture de sécurité.</p>","audioText":null},"possibleAnswers":[{"__typename":"Answer","_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d7c4","gapIndex":null,"learningId":489006,"audioText":null,"text":"uniquement le conducteur","isCorrect":true,"okulusAssets":[]},{"__typename":"Answer","_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d7c5","gapIndex":null,"learningId":490219,"audioText":null,"text":"le conducteur et le(s) passager(s) avant","isCorrect":false,"okulusAssets":[]},{"__typename":"Answer","_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d7c6","gapIndex":null,"learningId":491449,"audioText":null,"text":"le conducteur et tous ses passagers","isCorrect":false,"okulusAssets":[]}]}]},{"__typename":"Exercise","_id":"60b0bef6b80948a2bf97af52","learningId":151609,"text":"","difficulty":1,"displayType":"","audioText":"","maxDurationSeconds":0,"okulusAssets":[],"questionsData":[{"__typename":"Question","learningId":142701,"score":{"__typename":"Score","success":0,"failure":1},"type":"QCM_SINGLE","okulusAssets":[{"__typename":"File","_id":"4fcf5ce8-0340-446b-9cd1-10abe39f5837","version":"v0","mime":"image/jpeg","filename":"4fcf5ce8-0340-446b-9cd1-10abe39f5837","s3swhUrl":"https://diy7ta1tt6jst.cloudfront.net/prod/okulus/4fcf5ce8-0340-446b-9cd1-10abe39f5837","realm":"digiSchool","imageTags":{"__typename":"ImageTags","width":1224,"height":816,"format":"JPEG"}},{"__typename":"File","_id":"cef5262f-a98b-453e-83dc-036437af7d48","version":"v0","mime":"audio/mpeg","filename":"cef5262f-a98b-453e-83dc-036437af7d48","s3swhUrl":"https://diy7ta1tt6jst.cloudfront.net/prod/okulus/cef5262f-a98b-453e-83dc-036437af7d48","realm":"digiSchool","imageTags":null}],"_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d79f","text":"Une femme enceinte doit porter sa ceinture de sécurité :","audioText":null,"explanation":{"__typename":"Explanation","text":"<p>Même pour une femme enceinte, la dispense du port de la ceinture ne peut se faire que par une dérogation pour contre-indications médicales graves, officiellement délivrée par le Service Public Fédéral Mobilité.</p>","audioText":null},"possibleAnswers":[{"__typename":"Answer","_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d7c9","gapIndex":null,"learningId":489009,"audioText":null,"text":"oui, sauf si elle est en possession d'un certificat médical","isCorrect":false,"okulusAssets":[]},{"__typename":"Answer","_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d7ca","gapIndex":null,"learningId":490221,"audioText":null,"text":"oui, sauf si elle possède une dérogation délivrée par le Service fédéral de la Mobilité","isCorrect":true,"okulusAssets":[]},{"__typename":"Answer","_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d7cb","gapIndex":null,"learningId":491448,"audioText":null,"text":"non","isCorrect":false,"okulusAssets":[]}]}]},{"__typename":"Exercise","_id":"60b0bef6b80948a2bf97af68","learningId":151610,"text":"","difficulty":1,"displayType":"","audioText":"","maxDurationSeconds":0,"okulusAssets":[],"questionsData":[{"__typename":"Question","learningId":142702,"score":{"__typename":"Score","success":0,"failure":1},"type":"QCM_SINGLE","okulusAssets":[{"__typename":"File","_id":"22e9c94d-b27d-495f-b21d-4d408c5b7827","version":"v0","mime":"audio/mpeg","filename":"22e9c94d-b27d-495f-b21d-4d408c5b7827","s3swhUrl":"https://diy7ta1tt6jst.cloudfront.net/prod/okulus/22e9c94d-b27d-495f-b21d-4d408c5b7827","realm":"digiSchool","imageTags":null},{"__typename":"File","_id":"d4bedc41-a778-452f-a23d-f504aabd3569","version":"v0","mime":"image/jpeg","filename":"d4bedc41-a778-452f-a23d-f504aabd3569","s3swhUrl":"https://diy7ta1tt6jst.cloudfront.net/prod/okulus/d4bedc41-a778-452f-a23d-f504aabd3569","realm":"digiSchool","imageTags":{"__typename":"ImageTags","width":1224,"height":816,"format":"JPEG"}}],"_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d7a0","text":"Je mesure moins d'1,50 m et prends place à l'arrière d'une voiture. Je suis obligé de boucler la ceinture de sécurité :","audioText":null,"explanation":{"__typename":"Explanation","text":"<p>Sont dispensés de l'utilisation obligatoire de la ceinture de sécurité : 1° les conducteurs qui effectuent une marche arrière ; 2° les conducteurs de taxis, lorsqu'ils transportent un client ; 3° les conducteurs et les passagers des véhicules prioritaires lorsqu'ils transportent des personnes qui constituent une menace potentielle ou dans l'environnement immédiat du lieu de l'intervention ou lorsqu'ils donnent des soins à la personne transportée ; 4° les personnes détenant une dérogation pour contre-indications médicales graves ; 5° les agents de la Poste, dans le cadre de la distribution et de la levée du courrier. N.B.: La dispense du port de la ceinture pour les personnes mesurant moins de 1,50 m a été supprimée, tant pour le conducteur que les passagers.</p>","audioText":null},"possibleAnswers":[{"__typename":"Answer","_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d7ce","gapIndex":null,"learningId":489007,"audioText":null,"text":"oui","isCorrect":true,"okulusAssets":[]},{"__typename":"Answer","_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d7cf","gapIndex":null,"learningId":490220,"audioText":null,"text":"oui, sauf si je suis en possession d'un certificat médical","isCorrect":false,"okulusAssets":[]},{"__typename":"Answer","_id":"65e8356fdf882c852038d7d0","gapIndex":null,"learningId":491450,"audioText":null,"text":"non","isCorrect":false,"okulusAssets":[]}]}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}